reviewText: I own many of the Bike-O-Vision videos, most are very interesting to watch while I'm on the bike.  This was a newer film and had a couple of strong reviews, so I bought it.  My impression is that it is not even close to a good video; not quality wise, but content wise.
This is my 2nd video, makes stationary bike riding much more interesting.
Nice scenery; lively. . . like the music too!  Highly recommended.
